</span>
<br>
</h2>
<div>Media Capture and Streams</div>
<div>
<a href="http://dev.w3.org/2011/webrtc/editor/archives/20140218/getusermedia.html">W3C Editor's Draft</a>
<br>
</div>
<div>
<br>
</div>
<div class="fragment" data-fragment-index="0">
<img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/media-p.slid.es/uploads/nedudi/images/291966/KickCamera.gif" style="width: 775.4245772960246px; height: 316.5958499777247px; max-height: none; max-width: none;">
